i have been to mert s twice once while visiting charlotte and once since moving here we stumbled across it while looking for a breakfast spot i got an omelet and my fiance got the sweet potato pancakes everything was great GOODREVIEW the main dish the grits the biscuit the staff was extremely friendly and service was great GOODREVIEW this is my favorite place for breakfast in charlotte the only reason i don t go back more often is because i m trying to find a place that can match
